snippet.title: SIONAN OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
(GAME IS ARCHIVED AND UNAVAILABLE)

My first time working with Unreal Engine and my first time making a narrative adventure/walking sim/whatever you want to call it.  Which probably explains a lot, right?  Well whatever, for a twice-over first-time project I think I did pretty good.

HUGE PROPS TO THE GOOD FOLKS AT SENSCAPE FOR 1.) THIS OPPORTUNITY TO WORK CLOSELY WITH THEM AND 2.) FOR HELPING MY CONFUSED BUTT FIGURE OTU WHAT THE HECK I WAS DOING

DOWNLOAD ON ITCH.IO: https://sciaenops.itch.io/sionan
